info.name: Itis
info.description:
DESIGN BY:
Naoto Fukasawa

MATERIALS:
Painted zamak base; painted metal stem; painted metal and polycarbonate head; satin transparent polycarbonate diffuser. Two articulations connect the stem to the base and the head which allow the stem to be tilted from 0° to 90° and the head to be rotated 180°.

INFORMATIONS:
Led Total power 5,4Wn
warm white 3000Kn
Lighting Output 220 lm, Dimmable
